          >
        </li>
        <li>
          Microsoft Edge:
          <a href="https://privacy.microsoft.com/es-es/windows-10-microsoft-edge-and-privacy" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"
            >https://privacy.microsoft.com/es-es/windows-10-microsoft-edge-and-privacy</a
          >
        </li>
        <li>
          Chrome:
          <a
            href="https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95647?co=GENIE.Platform%3DDesktop&hl=es"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            target="_blank">https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95647</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          Firefox:
          <a href="https://support.mozilla.org/es/kb/Borrar%20cookies" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"
            >https://support.mozilla.org/es/kb/Borrar cookies</a
          >
        </li>
        <li>
